title: HOUR 3- Todd Gurley and Dan Hicks 081420
itunes:title: HOUR 3- Todd Gurley and Dan Hicks 081420
description:
Todd Gurley walks Dan through a day with all the covid restrictions. Todd says this period is very hard on rookies because they are so limited in being able to show what they can do at real speed. Gurley, who played at Georgia, is glad to be playing with the Falcons. Dan Hicks gives Dan some insight on the golf caddy who cost his golfer a chance to win.
